;; hinagata 雛形 — seed legal-template-commons graph (real, PUBLIC reference data only)
;; ADR-2606111954 · vocabulary: legal-template-ontology (00-contracts/schemas/legal-template-ontology.kotoba.edn)
;;
;; SCOPE GUARD (constitutional, G1 — read first):
;;   - hinagata is a COMMONS of fair, openly-licensed legal-document templates that ANYONE
;;     may copy + adapt, NEVER the practice of law. NO advice, NO opinion on a specific
;;     matter, NO representation, NO enforceability certification. UPL is structurally
;;     excluded: the unit is ALWAYS a template / clause / statute-link — never a party,
;;     a matter, or a recommendation.
;;   - A clause's :cites-statute / :mandated-by link is a DISCLOSED STRUCTURAL FACT (this
;;     clause rests on this public article), sourced from the instrument or its official
;;     guidance — never a hinagata verdict that the clause is valid/sufficient (N3).
;;   - The lens is integrated STATUTORY GROUNDEDNESS over a template, routed to PUBLIC
;;     RELEASE (free use). karma lives ONLY on edges (:en/binding-load × disclosed
;;     :clause/optionality; N1).
;;
;; SOURCING: statute citations, instrument names and official source URLs are :authoritative
;;   publicly-disclosed facts (EUR-Lex / e-Gov / UNCITRAL / ILO / treaty depositaries). The
;;   template TEXT bodies are :representative — fair illustrative drafts published under
;;   Apache-2.0 + Charter Rider, NOT exhaustive and NOT certified for any jurisdiction.
;;   Coverage of all template families / all jurisdictions is ~0 by design. Live legal-corpus
;;   binding (ADR-2605262800) + Council review is G7-gated.
;;
;; LAW IS PLURAL, NOT ONE SYSTEM: the seed spans international treaties / model laws (CISG,
;;   New York Convention, UNCITRAL, ILO, eIDAS, ESIGN/UETA), civil-law (JP 民法 / 借地借家法 /
;;   利息制限法 / 特定商取引法 / 電子署名法; EU GDPR), and open-source license law (Apache-2.0).

